            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " object to this property causes the app’s interface elements to adopt the specified appearance instead. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Individual windows and views may still override the app’s appearance to customize their own appearance."
